Summary: Ctrl-PgUp and Ctrl-PgDn scrolling should be configurable
Class: bug
Priority: medium
Difficulty: fun
Present-in: 0.54 0.55 0.56 0.57 0.58 0.59 0.60
Content-Type: text/x-html-body

<p>Since we implemented <a href="ctrl-pgupdn.html">ctrl-pgupdn</a>
Ctrl-PgUp and Ctrl-PgDn scroll by one line at a time.
</p>
<p>
Some people / applications now expect these keys to generate escape
sequences, so this behaviour should be configurable.
</p>
